# Changelog conventions

Format follows [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/) and [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## Entry format

```markdown
## [x.y.z] - YYYY-MM-DD

### Added
- `ClassName::method(signature)` — plain-English description.

### Changed
### Fixed
### Removed
```

- Use only the sections that are relevant; omit empty ones.
- One bullet per change; lead with a backtick-quoted symbol when referring to code.
- Keep bullets short — what changed and why, not how.
- New versions go at the top, above older entries.
- Never edit or backdate a released version entry.
